content.rendered:
Directed by Pradeep Sarkar

Written by Anand Gandhi. Mitesh Shah

Cast Kajol (Eela Raiturkar). Riddhi Sen (Vivaan). Tota Roy Chowdhury (Arun). Neha Dhupia (Padma) . R.J. Alok (Self – Professor). Babita Anant (Society Member). Ila Arun (Self (Cameo)). Amitabh Bachchan (Self (Cameo)). Muskaan Bamne (Deepti). Sushmita Bhandari (Nidhi). Mahesh Bhatt (Self (Cameo)). Bhaweeka Chaudhary (Monisha). Alisha Chinai (Self (Cameo) (as Alisha Chinoi)). Shataf Figar (Madhavi). Daanish Gandhi (Guy in the theatre). Ajitesh Gupta (Student Leader). Zakir Hussain (Principal Vivek Joshi). Atul Kulkarni (Prime Minister). Intekhab Mahmood (Volunteer in Event). Rashi Mal (Nikita). Chirag Malhotra (Yash). Anu Malik (Self (Cameo)). Sanjay Paraswani (Hotel Owner). Mukesh Rishi (Rajesh Kumar Sharma). Baba Sehgal (Self (Cameo)). Shaan (Self (Cameo)).Aamir Shaikh. Shubam Sharma (Shubham). Shivani Sopori (Society Member (as Shivaani Sopuri)). Gaurri Sukhtankar (Teacher (as Gauri Sukhtankar)). Ram Manohar Yadav (College student for audition (as himself))

Language Hindi

Producers Ajay Devgn. Akshay Gada. Dhaval Gada. Kushal Gada. Neeraj Gala. Reshmaa Kadakia. Kunjan Oza. Sanjay Paraswani. Kumar Mangat Pathak. Vikrant Sharma. Tarlok Singh

Production Ajay Devgn Ffilm. Pen Studio
